sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Attacker (Tenant A)
    participant API as Shared API
    participant Cache as Shared Cache
    participant DB as Shared DB

    A->>API: Request invoice id=42
    API->>Cache: GET invoice:42 (missing tenant namespace)
    Cache-->>API: Cached object from Tenant B
    API-->>A: Returns Tenant B invoice

    A->>API: Update id=42 with weak scope check
    API->>DB: UPDATE invoices SET ... WHERE id=42
    DB-->>API: Success (cross-tenant write)
